{"tid":639149,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"$2.5 的回憶","createTime":"2018-04-23T09:23:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T09:44:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eb00d76ec8de90cbcb54b1c04c4506d5357e7cbe","tid":639149,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:23:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.thestandnews.com/澳門/2-5的回憶/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%2F2-5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%2F&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=2e65b006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%2F2-5%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%2F&h=e1e48af9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thestandnews.com/澳門/2-5的回憶/</a><br />\n<br />\n$2.5 的回憶<br />\n蕭家怡2018/4/23 &mdash; 16:02<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/aoyu_Qionn_1200x0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Faoyu_Qionn_1200x0.PNG&h=8da693f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五日前，澳門政府公報刊登行政長官批示，公佈巴士將於4月21日起加價，正價一律收費6元，而使用澳門通則收費3元。<br />\n<br />\n想着這6元一程的巴士，我突然想起了小時候乘巴士上學的情景，那時候，一程巴士的價格是2.5元。<br />\n<br />\n我的小學離家相當近，就是走路也不必5分鐘，也許是因為這樣，我相當羨慕可以乘巴士上學的同學，而他們那張澳巴月票，更是我心目中的「身分象徵」；後來升上中學，學校離家的路程其實也是20分鐘左右，但口袋有了零錢，有了自己出門的自由，我終於可以過過巴士癮，而我乘搭的19號巴士，正正就是相片中的這款。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n時代變了，這款車早已不復見，連車費都漲了一倍以上，2.5元一程的巴士，就留在回憶吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面書專頁：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alvissio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falvissio&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=8b52fe8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/alvissio</a><br />\n<br />\nMedium：<a href=\"https://medium.com/@alvissio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40alvissio&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=d350cc16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@alvissio</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/alvissio/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Falvissio%2F&d=wH3wEsOnesGP%2BWOuAQRlR9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=48bdff96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/alvissio/</a>"},{"pid":"7c01a0428eeb39387320a84baa0a2ea3d0379312","tid":639149,"uid":93839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:44:34.000Z","msg":"逼人用澳門通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}